# Active Directory — Account Locked

## Steps
1. Verified lockout in ADUC  
2. Checked Event Viewer logs  
3. Reset password  
4. Cleared mapped drive credentials  
5. Cleared cached logins  

## Resolution
Password reset + cleared stale sessions → user logged in successfully.

# Password Reset & Sync Issues

## Steps
1. Reset password in AD  
2. Forced sync through Azure AD  
3. Verified MFA status  
4. Cleared cached credentials  

## Resolution
Password reset propagated → login successful.

# MFA Not Working

## Symptoms
- User stuck on MFA screen
- App never receives prompt

## Diagnostics
1. Verified phone number  
2. Checked Authenticator app  
3. Verified network connection  
4. Reset MFA registration  

## Resolution
Removed old device → re-enrolled → MFA functioning normally.
